OL,3,CWoman, 25, charged with attempted
OL,4,Cmurder after tram stop attack
OL,6,FA woman has been charged with
OL,7,Fattempted murder following an attack
OL,8,Fon another woman at a tram stop in
OL,9,FManchester.
OL,11,FThe victim, in her 30s, suffered a
OL,12,Flaceration to her head in the assault
OL,13,Fat West Didsbury tram station on
OL,14,FLapwing Lane at about 11:45pm on
OL,15,FWednesday.
OL,17,FKeida Finlayson, 25, of Victoria
OL,18,FCrescent, Manchester, has been charged
OL,19,Fwith attempted murder and assault for
OL,20,Fan unrelated incident.
